item.description: cdsctl group token generate Generate a new token Synopsis Generate a new token cdsctl group token generate GROUPNAME EXPIRATION [flags] Options --format string Output format: plain|json|yaml (default "plain") -h, --help help for generate Options inherited from parent commands -f, --file string set configuration file -k, --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers. -w, --no-warnings do not display warnings -v, --verbose verbose output SEE ALSO cdsctl group token - Manage CDS group token
